Description: CryoSPARC .cs metadata reader for MDSPACE
 Converts CryoSPARC particle Dataset files into an MDSPACE-compatible
 tab-separated metadata representation.
 .
 The executable is compiled with Nuitka and includes its private Python
 runtime and required Python modules. Python is not required at runtime.
